snippet.title: Joggernauts Coming Oct 11th to Nintendo Switch and Steam
snippet.description:
Jog! Jump! Switch! Coordinate the crazy conga line of alien athletes in this autorunner / puzzle platformer for 1-4 players.

Coming October 11th, 2018 to Nintendo Switch, PC, and Mac!

Wishlist now on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/747620/Joggernauts/
